        <name>XV_letterbox_LookupConfig</name>
        <param>
          <type>UINTPTR</type>
          <declname>BaseAddress</declname>
        </param>
        <briefdescription>
<para>XV_letterbox_LookupConfig - Looks up the configuration for a <ref refid="struct_x_v__letterbox" kindref="compound">XV_letterbox</ref> instance based on the provided BaseAddress. </para>        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This function iterates through the XV_letterbox_ConfigTable to find a configuration entry whose BaseAddress matches the given BaseAddress. If a match is found, a pointer to the configuration structure is returned. If BaseAddress is zero or NULL, the function returns the first configuration entry. If no match is found, NULL is returned.</para><para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>BaseAddress</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>is the base address of the <ref refid="struct_x_v__letterbox" kindref="compound">XV_letterbox</ref> instance to look up.</para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>A pointer to the configuration structure if a match is found, otherwise NULL. </para></simplesect>
</para>        </detaileddescription>
        <inbodydescription>
        </inbodydescription>
